snippet.title: SAVY Writes Books
snippet.description:
A booktube, authortube, and art channel that features lots of cute dogs.
SAVY talks about writing, gives book reviews, and delves into the process of writing and publishing books from the perspective of someone who has started their own book business.
SAVY is the author of the contemporary new-adult novel Sculpt Yourself, a body-positive LGBT+ romance with a sci-fi twist, as well as the Furever Home Friends children's book series based on the stories of real rescue dogs.
SAVY's goal is to be so cute and upbeat that for a second you'll forget how crude she's being.
